{
  "texts": [
    "This protest, which I attended as part of my fieldwork on digital rights, prompted the questions over AI, ethics and the environment that I explore in this article.",
    "But how do World Water Day, Chile and AI connect in the first place?",
    "Part of the answer lies on the group that invited me to join the rally: MOSACAT.",
    "1 This organisation, whose members I had met a few weeks before, had formed an opposition to the construction of a water-intensive Google data centre in the working-class area of Cerrillos in Santiago.",
    "A month after this protest, I also engaged with the Council of Atacameno Peoples ('the Council' hereafter), which reunites 18 Lickan Antay communities resisting water-intensive lithium extraction in the Atacama Desert."
  ]
}